---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import NetworkLogo from '../components/NetworkLogo.jsx';
---

<Layout title="SUDATA | Data Science Society">
	<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[50vh] text-center space-y-12 pt-32 pb-24">
		<div class="w-full h-[400px] mb-16 relative z-10">
			<NetworkLogo client:only="react" />
		</div>
		
		<!-- Headline: Solid Electric Blue, Neon Tube Glow -->
		<h1 class="reveal-on-scroll text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-sudata-neon tracking-widest mb-12 neon-text-shadow">
			Data is the DNA of the Modern World
		</h1>
		
		<div class="reveal-on-scroll max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-48 px-6">
			<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-sudata-grey font-mono-tech leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-sudata-neon pl-8 text-left">
				<span class="text-sudata-neon font-bold animate-flicker">&gt;_</span> At SUDATA, we believe understanding data isn't just about gradesâ€”it's about navigating the information age. We welcome students of ANY discipline to join us, so long as you want to know a little more about data.
			</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-16 w-full max-w-[90rem] px-8">
			<!-- Card 1: Hub -->
			<div class="reveal-on-scroll group glass-panel-3d p-12 flex flex-col items-start text-left h-full relative overflow-hidden scanline-overlay">
				
				<div class="relative z-10 mb-10 font-mono-tech text-sudata-neon text-sm tracking-[0.2em] opacity-80">
					[ 01_HUB ]
				</div>
				
				<div class="relative z-10 mb-10 text-sudata-neon text-6xl font-mono neon-icon-glow flex justify-center w-full">
					<span class="font-mono text-white/50 mr-6 text-7xl">[</span>
                    <!-- Pixel Brain SVG (Custom 32x32 Grid - "brain" missing in pixelarticons v1.8.1) -->
					<svg width="96" height="96" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-sudata-neon" style="filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px #00F0FF);">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M10 6H22V8H24V10H26V18H24V22H20V24H14V26H10V22H8V18H6V10H8V8H10V6ZM12 10H14V12H12V10ZM18 10H20V12H18V10ZM22 14H24V16H22V14ZM8 14H10V16H8V14ZM12 18H14V20H12V18ZM18 18H20V20H18V18Z" fill="#00F0FF"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="font-mono text-white/50 ml-6 text-7xl">]</span>
				</div>
				
				<h2 class="relative z-10 text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-widest group-hover:text-sudata-neon transition-colors">
					The Hub
				</h2>
				<p class="relative z-10 text-base font-mono-tech text-sudata-grey/90 leading-relaxed">
					Share and learn data-related knowledge. From Python scripts to neural networks, we cover it all.
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Card 2: Collective -->
			<div class="reveal-on-scroll group glass-panel-3d p-12 flex flex-col items-start text-left h-full relative overflow-hidden delay-100 scanline-overlay">

				<div class="relative z-10 mb-10 font-mono-tech text-sudata-neon text-sm tracking-[0.2em] opacity-80">
					[ 02_COLLECTIVE ]
				</div>

				<div class="relative z-10 mb-10 text-sudata-neon text-6xl font-mono neon-icon-glow flex justify-center w-full">
					<span class="font-mono text-white/50 mr-6 text-7xl">[</span>
                    <!-- Pixel Users SVG (pixelarticons) -->
                    <svg width="96" height="96" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-sudata-neon" style="filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px #00F0FF);">
                        <path d="M11 0H5v2H3v6h2v2h6V8H5V2h6V0zm0 2h2v6h-2V2zM0 14h2v4h12v2H0v-6zm2 0h12v-2H2v2zm14 0h-2v6h2v-6zM15 0h4v2h-4V0zm4 8h-4v2h4V8zm0-6h2v6h-2V2zm5 12h-2v4h-4v2h6v-6zm-6-2h4v2h-4v-2z" fill="#00F0FF"/>
                    </svg>
					<span class="font-mono text-white/50 ml-6 text-7xl">]</span>
				</div>
				<h2 class="relative z-10 text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-widest group-hover:text-sudata-neon transition-colors">
					The Collective
				</h2>
				<p class="relative z-10 text-base font-mono-tech text-sudata-grey/90 leading-relaxed">
					Hang out with savvy people and make friends. Collaboration is key in the data world.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Card 3: Blast -->
			<div class="reveal-on-scroll group glass-panel-3d p-12 flex flex-col items-start text-left h-full relative overflow-hidden delay-200 scanline-overlay">

				<div class="relative z-10 mb-10 font-mono-tech text-sudata-neon text-sm tracking-[0.2em] opacity-80">
					[ 03_BLAST ]
				</div>

				<div class="relative z-10 mb-10 text-sudata-neon text-6xl font-mono neon-icon-glow flex justify-center w-full">
					<span class="font-mono text-white/50 mr-6 text-7xl">[</span>
                    <!-- Pixel Zap SVG (pixelarticons) -->
                    <svg width="96" height="96" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-sudata-neon" style="filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px #00F0FF);">
                        <path d="M12 1h2v8h8v4h-2v-2h-8V5h-2V3h2V1zM8 7V5h2v2H8zM6 9V7h2v2H6zm-2 2V9h2v2H4zm10 8v2h-2v2h-2v-8H2v-4h2v2h8v6h2zm2-2v2h-2v-2h2zm2-2v2h-2v-2h2zm0 0h2v-2h-2v2z" fill="#00F0FF"/>
                    </svg>
					<span class="font-mono text-white/50 ml-6 text-7xl">]</span>
				</div>
				<h2 class="relative z-10 text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-widest group-hover:text-sudata-neon transition-colors">
					The Blast
				</h2>
				<p class="relative z-10 text-base font-mono-tech text-sudata-grey/90 leading-relaxed">
					Have fun while exploring the info-rich world. Hackathons, workshops, and more.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- CTA Section -->
		<div class="reveal-on-scroll mt-64 w-full max-w-5xl text-center space-y-20 mb-48 px-4">
			<h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white font-mono-tech tracking-widest flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
				Why not join us if you want to hang out with other savvy people like yourself? 
                <!-- Pixel Link SVG (pixelarticons) -->
                <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-sudata-neon inline-block" style="image-rendering: pixelated; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 5px #00F0FF);">
                    <path d="M4 6h7v2H4v8h7v2H2V6h2zm16 0h-7v2h7v8h-7v2h9V6h-2zm-3 5H7v2h10v-2z" fill="#00F0FF"/>
                </svg>
			</h3>
			
			<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-16">
				<a href="https://usu.edu.au/clubs/sydney-uni-data-society/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" 
				   class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-14 py-7 font-mono-tech font-bold text-white text-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-white/30 hover:border-sudata-neon/80 bg-transparent rounded-xl overflow-hidden btn-scanline">
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-sudata-neon/10 translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300 ease-out"></div>
					<span class="relative flex items-center gap-4 group-hover:tracking-wider transition-all duration-300">
						Official USU Membership 
                        <!-- Pixel Briefcase SVG (pixelarticons) -->
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-sudata-neon animate-pulse" style="image-rendering: pixelated; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 5px #00F0FF);">
                            <path d="M8 3h8v4h6v14H2V7h6V3zm2 4h4V5h-4v2zM4 9v10h16V9H4z" fill="#00F0FF"/>
                        </svg>
					</span>
				</a>

				<a href="https://www.instagram.com/usyd.sudata/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
				   class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-14 py-7 font-mono-tech font-bold text-sudata-navy text-lg transition-all duration-300 bg-sudata-neon hover:bg-[#70FFFF] rounded-xl shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,240,255,0.6)] hover:shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(0,240,255,1)] btn-scanline hover:-translate-y-1">
					<span class="relative flex items-center gap-4">
						Follow the Gram 
                        <!-- Pixel Layout/Instagram SVG (pixelarticons fallback - "layout-header" looks close to ig logo if instagram missing, but user provided path above) -->
                         <!-- Wait, I found the path in the previous step, let me use that exact path if available or closest. 
                              Actually, previous step for instagram.svg failed.
                              Let's use 'camera-alt' or construct a pixel instagram icon manually if needed.
                              Wait, I can use the 'camera' icon from pixelarticons if instagram is missing, or build it. 
                              Actually, let's look at the available icons list again. 
                              'camera-alt.svg', 'camera.svg', 'image.svg'.
                              Let's try to find a suitable replacement or just draw a pixel art instagram logo since I can't read the file.
                              
                              Actually, the user asked to replace 'satellite' with 'instagram'. I should try to find if it exists.
                              The list_dir showed 486 files. I don't see 'instagram.svg' in the list I got.
                              I see 'mastodon.svg', 'github.svg'.
                              Maybe it is under a different name?
                              'camera' is a good fallback. 
                              BUT, I can also just create a simple pixel art instagram logo path.
                              Instagram logo is a square with a circle inside and a dot.
                              
                              Let's use a custom pixel path for Instagram since it's likely missing from this specific version or named differently.
                              
                              Path for Pixel Art Instagram (24x24):
                              Outer box: 2-22 x 2-22
                              Inner box/ring
                              Dot at top right
                          -->
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-sudata-navy" style="image-rendering: pixelated;">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 2H17V4H19V6H21V18H19V20H17V22H7V20H5V18H3V6H5V4H7V2ZM7 4H5V6H7V4ZM17 4H19V6H17V4ZM19 18V6H21V18H19ZM17 20V18H19V20H17ZM7 20H17V18H7V20ZM5 18V20H7V18H5ZM5 6V18H3V6H5ZM9 8H15V10H17V14H15V16H9V14H7V10H9V8ZM11 10H13V14H11V10ZM17 6H19V8H17V6Z" fill="#020617"/>
                        </svg>
					</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
